<paragraph id="A8444739F29041DD13CC0AF7E3ECAC9B" pageId="177" pageNumber="178">
Canary Islands: Gran Canaria, Fuerteventura (
<emphasis id="F2CD92AD7B854826B090D71FA04F15F0" italics="true" pageId="177" pageNumber="178">
Carine &amp; 
<normalizedToken id="7E6C339F37AC9659589739BF48E759C0" originalValue="Durães">Duraes</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
158, 
<emphasis id="106782768DAC0DB7DEFC11B37FBFC9D6" italics="true" pageId="177" pageNumber="178">Bramwell &amp; Humphries</emphasis>
3095, 
<emphasis id="4EC0516A207E169B0071BCE9DD1BE0EE" italics="true" pageId="177" pageNumber="178">Kunkel</emphasis>
13, 
<emphasis id="B4A86542333D346818A7790EEC7526D6" italics="true" pageId="177" pageNumber="178">Beckett</emphasis>
736; 
<emphasis id="A3D4EDE372CE88FAA46B7BD3DD2A9EA3" italics="true" pageId="177" pageNumber="178">Peck</emphasis>
5). Globally rare.
</paragraph>
